SOLUTIION
Issue Description:
Unable to receive invitation or alerts emails for any users from web application " http://sharepoint "
Possible Cause:
Use TLS Connection Encryption, Setting was not proper 
 
Resolution Summary:
 
· in Central Administration’ s Application Management > Web Application > Manage Web Application
· Select web application http://sharepoint 
· General Settings > Outgoing Email >Use TLS Connection Encryption : No
· We change value for  Use TLS Connection Encryption = YES 
· After making this change issue got resolved 
